# Testing Rule

- Write pytest-compatible tests for every new function and agent.
- Mock external API calls (EDGAR, Wikipedia/search APIs) in all unit tests.
- Structure tests using Arrange / Act / Assert comments.
- Generate a corresponding test stub whenever a new agent or tool module is created.
- Include at least one happy path and one error/edge case per function.

